title: Sons Of Anarchy Season 6
description:
Sons.of.Anarchy.S06E01.Straw
As Jax continues to push the club into more legitimate 

businesses he can't escape the sins of SAMCRO's past. 
Aired September 10th, 2013

Sons.of.Anarchy.S06E02.One One Six
ax deals with collateral damage as external pressure continue 

to stack up against SAMCRO.
Aired Steptember 17th, 2013
 
Sons.of.Anarchy.S06E03.Poenitentia
Jax secures a new alliance for the club while Clay makes moves 

inside for protection. 
Aired September 24th, 2013

Sons.of.Anarchy.S06E04.Wolfs Angel
An attack at the compound leads SOA to seek revenge. 
Aired OCtober 1st, 2013

Sons.of.Anarchy.S06E05.The Mad King
The club is forced to make an uneasy alliance with unforeseen 

consequences. 
Aired October 8th, 2013

Sons.of.Anarchy.S06E06.Salvage
Jax and the MC must confront their past and choose their 

future.
Aired October 15th, 2013

Sons.of.Anarchy.S06E07.Sweet And Vaded
Triggers are pulled that strengthen the MC, but also threaten 

to destroy it. 
Aired October 22nd, 2013

Sons.of.Anarchy.S06E08.Los Fantasmas
Pressure mounts on Jax as the sins of his club and family pull 

him in different directions.
Aired October 29th, 2013

Sons.of.Anarchy.S06E09.John 8:32
Jax learns new secrets that turn his world sideways. 
Aired November 5th, 2013

Sons.of.Anarchy.S06E10.Huang Wu
Jax looks to push the club forward but the Irish put another 

obstacle in his way. 
Aired November 12th, 2013

Sons.of.Anarchy.S06E11.Aon Rud Persanta
Tension mounts as the club makes a bold move to finally get 

out of guns. 
Aired November 19th,2013

Sons.of.Anarchy.S06E12.You Are My SunShine
As the dust beings to settle, Jax's world is suddenly turned 

upside down.
Aired December 3rd, 2013

Sons.of.Anarchy.S06E13.A Mother's Work
Jax has to handle some unhappy customers as the weapon deal 

goes through Mike's organization. Meanwhile, Tara finds a way 

to avoid jail without giving up the MC. 
Aired December 10th, 2013

About:
A man in his early 30s struggles to find a balance in his life between being a new dad and his involvement in a motorcycle club.
